  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc0\u0b95 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil has no moral right to hold office as President - Vasu",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "We have decided to carry out extensive negotiations with all the candidates contesting for the election of the new President.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe has no moral right to continue as president, said Vasudeva Nanayakkara, leader of the Left Jananaya Front.",
        "It has been mentioned that four people are contesting for the vacant post of the President. It will be clear how many people are contesting only after the nominations which will be held after the parliamentary session to be held tomorrow.",
        "It is necessary to find a solution to the basic problems found in the social structure. If you act based on political objectives, you will not be able to solve any problems.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe has no moral right to continue as President.",
        "It is completely contrary to the Lok Sabha for a person who was ignored by the people in the general election to act as the first citizen of the country.",
        "Following the election of the new president, we insist that a national government should be formed instead of a Podujana Peramuna-led government.",
        "All political parties should act in common harmony to solve political and social problems.",
        "Podujana Peramuna's General Secretary Sagara Kariyawasam has denied that Podujana Peramuna's General Secretary GL Peiris has denied that Podujana Peramuna will support the acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "He said that one of the many factors that led to the fall of the Podujana Peramuna-led government should be cited as one of the factors that led to the fall of the party's general secretary Sagara Kariyavasa."
      ],
